name: GPT-5 Chat Latest
description: GPT-5 Chat Latest is an alias pointing to the latest GPT-5 model optimized for chat and conversational applications. It automatically updates to use the most recent GPT-5 version, ensuring access to the latest improvements and capabilities.
notes: Dynamic alias that always points to the current GPT-5 model. Provides the same capabilities as GPT-5 with automatic version updates. Ideal for applications that want to stay current without manually updating model versions.
